OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FEngland's secondary schools
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fcausing concern            
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Some older pupils in England are       
OL,6, refusing to take lateral flow tests and
OL,7, wear face coverings in classrooms as   
OL,8, they head back to school, parents and  
OL,9, other pupils say.                      
OL,11,FCharities say they are worried about   
OL,12,Fthe effects on vulnerable students of  
OL,13,Fthis advice being ignored.             
OL,15,FHowever, other parents say masks impact
OL,16,Fon their children's learning.          
OL,18,FThe government says schools "can decide
OL,19,Fhow best to encourage" pupils to take  
OL,20,Ftests and wear masks.                  
